Excuse me for a second.

74
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,338
Hello.

75
00:12:20,447 --> 00:12:21,607
Travis?

76
00:12:22,483 --> 00:12:23,848
Guess who.

77
00:12:35,863 --> 00:12:36,852
Sir.

78
00:12:41,302 --> 00:12:42,360
Hello?

79
00:12:42,436 --> 00:12:45,928
Okay, baby, I need you and your team
up on him the second he leaves here.

80
00:12:46,006 --> 00:12:47,530
All the usual assets?

81
00:12:47,641 --> 00:12:50,235
- Of course, baby, anything you need.
- Good.

82
00:12:50,477 --> 00:12:53,310
I'll be in touch. And don't call me "baby."

83
00:13:01,789 --> 00:13:03,916
That would be meant for me.

84
00:13:03,991 --> 00:13:06,118
- You two know each other?
- Yeah.

85
00:13:06,593 --> 00:13:08,322
